Package hu.bme.mit.theta.litmus2xcfa.dsl.gen

Interface LitmusX86Listener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
LitmusX86BaseListener
public interface LitmusX86Listener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by LitmusX86Parser.
